                    "size": "large",
                    "color": "attention"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "TextBlock",
                    "text": "Even though the gold graphite shark is the most friendly kind, other sharks could be really dangerous!",
                    "wrap": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "TextBlock",
                    "text": "How about I find you a different location close by?",
